<section class="animate-fade">
  <h2>Inherintance</h2>
  <p>Inherintance allows a class to acquire properties and methods from another class.</p>

  <h3>Example:</h3>
  <pre>
class vehicle {
  int speed;
}
class Car extends Vehicle {
  int wheels;

}
 </pre>
